民情指數」，民研 9 月下旬由訪問員以隨機抽樣電話訪問方式，成功訪問 1013 名香港居民。結果顯示，行政長官林鄭月娥的評分為 27.5 分，評分與半個月前相比下跌 0.5 分。她的支持率則為 17 %，跌 3 個百分點，民望淨值為負 54 個百分點，跌 5 個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/chi/press-release/2020/20200929-chi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fchi%2Fpress-release%2F2020%2F20200929-chi&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=919d0c51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/chi/press-release/2020/20200929-chi</a>"},{"pid":"52b7f7f2f40688d4085b19cc0e5f1aebee1a8667","tid":2223094,"uid":263150,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0a2nNvw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0a2nNvw.jpg&h=72e2f3d7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"013abc048a0b8c23459b2e097f16b79dc0a36423","tid":2223094,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"之前嘅回升係咪誤差內？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844bf94d56f20c452c11a59bfd594906958c8587","tid":2223094,"uid":189046,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:27:08.000Z","msg":"被美國制裁的林鄭"},{"pid":"9e1689b89ea2ef8447f5beb8a8566df1c52df4c2","tid":2223094,"uid":63838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:30:46.000Z","msg":"少咗咁多示威都可以繼續跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca992d39422780ddee4cecadf9297d85c69ad43","tid":2223094,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e1689b89ea2ef8447f5beb8a8566df1c52df4c2","tid":2223094,"uid":63838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:30:46.000Z","msg":"少咗咁多示威都可以繼續跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" 